Package: powers
Type: Package
Title: Convenient Computation of Powers including the family of Box-Cox transformations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Vincenzo", "Coia", email="vincen.coia@stat.ubc.ca",
    role=c("aut", "cre")), person("Malcolm", "Bowles", email="mbowles@math.ubc.ca",
    role=c("ctb")))
Description: Are you tired of using the power operator in R?
    Use this package to call functions that apply common powers
    to your vectors, or to compute Box-Cox transformations.
